title: FREE: Week Eight Football Games to Watch
text:
FREE: Week Eight Football Games to Watch Luke Feddersen IowaPreps.com Editor 
Iowa Preps has put together a list of the games to watch this weekend on the football field. See which contests will be ones to keep a close eye as clubs are fighting it out on the gridiron now! 
Top 10 Games to Watch 
1.) Cedar Rapids Xavier at Iowa City Regina 2.) Independence at West Delaware 3.) Fort Dodge at Waukee 4.) Harlan at Glenwood 6.) Cedar Falls at Cedar Rapids, Kennedy 7.) PCM, Monroe at Albia8.) Williamsburg at Central Lee9.) Ankeny Centennial at Valley, West Des Moines10.) Gilbert at Grinnell
